[SHORT DESC]
10% chance to confuse.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 10% chance to confuse the target.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Confusion is the weakest Psychic-type move available, and with the existence of Psychic as a more powerful version, more easily available option which has a chance of lowering Special, there is literally no reason to use Confusion in a competitive environment.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/rb/moves/psychic">Psychic</a> is a stronger alternative with 90 Base Power which has a 30% chance of lowering Special by one stage.</p>